OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudy across all parts through the
OL,7,Fevening with outbreaks of mainly light
OL,8,Frain spreading east overnight. Chance
OL,9,Fof some heavier bursts of rain in the
OL,10,Ffar west after dawn. Breezy and
OL,11,Fstaying mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FCloudy with some intermittent
OL,14,Frain at first. Persistent rain with
OL,15,Fembedded heavier pulses, spreads east
OL,16,Fduring the morning and early
OL,17,Fafternoon, followed by brighter
OL,18,Fconditions and scattered, possibly
OL,19,Fthundery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
